            <p class="comment-content">唯一的缺憾是缺少古希腊古罗马和中世纪的内容。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="872746891">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-872746891" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-872746891" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="872746891">有用</a>
